name: motherhood #1
description:
On my second account on tezos blockchain, my first project this time has the theme of motherhood. The idea of creation is inspired from my daily life as a mother. The plan is that this first project will consist of 9 digital painting series. There is also a manual version of this work; with gouache technique.

Motherhood #1 representation “every night I reading fairytales for my daughter before going to bed, and I love this moment”
